on |url=http://kpopherald.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=201704041531000415545_2 |title=JYP to produce a web drama starring star-studded cast |access-date=4 April 2017 |publisher=Herald Corporation |website=Kpop Herald}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://entertain.naver.com/now/read?oid=382&aid=0000554229 |title=\ubc15\uc9c4\uc601\u00b7\uc724\ubc15\u00b7\ub2c9\ucfe4\u00b7\ub958\uc2b9\uc218\u00b7\uc2e0\uc740\uc218, \u2018\ub9c8\uc220\ud559\uad50\u2019 \ucd9c\uc5f0 \ud655\uc815 [\uacf5\uc2dd] |date=4 April 2017 |access-date=3 August 2017 |language=ko |trans-title=Park Jin Young, Yoon Bak, Nichkhun, Ryu Seung-soo, Shin Eun-su, 'Magic School' appearance confirmed [Official] |website=Sports Donga}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Film===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[A Stray Goat]]''\n| Jo Min-sik\n| Movie debut\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''Princess Aya ''\n| Prince Bari\n| animated, Korean dubbed<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://news.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2019/10/05/2019100501405.html |title='\ud504\ub9b0\uc138\uc2a4 \uc544\uc57c' \uac13\uc138\ube10 \uc9c4\uc601 \"\uccab \ub354\ube59, \uac1c\ubd09\ud558\uba74 \ub3c8 \ub0b4\uace0 \ubcfc \uc608\uc815\" [24th BIFF] |date=2019-10-05 |website=news.chosun.com |language=ko |access-date=2020-01-11}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''The Angel Without, The Devil Within ''\n| Jung-dae\n| <ref>{{Cite news |last=\uae40\ub098\ub77c \uae30\uc790 |url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/117/0003317918 |title='\uc57c\ucc28', \uc624\ub298(31\uc77c) \ud06c\ub7ad\ud06c\uc778\u2026\"\uc124\uacbd\uad6cX\ubc15\ud574\uc218\u2192\uac13\uc138\ube10 \uc9c4\uc601 \ub4f1 \ud569\ub958\" [\uacf5\uc2dd] |date=December 31, 2019 |language=ko |website=Naver}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n===Hosting===\n<!--Only permanent MC jobs, no one time appearances.-->\n{| class=\"wikitable\"  border=\"1\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Channel\n! Show\n! Ref\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\"| 2015-2016\n| [[Mnet (TV channel)|Mnet]] \n| ''[[M! Countdown]]''\n|<ref name=\"mdown\" />\n|-\n| 20